thread.title: Four migrants in critical condition after Calais shooting

title: Four migrants in critical condition after Calais shooting
text:
Four migrants in critical condition after Calais shooting Friday, February 02, 2018 - 00:49 
A brawl between Eritrean and Afghan migrants in the French port city of Calais has resulted in four critical injuries from gunshot wounds. The port has born the brunt of France's migrant crisis.
